title: Varela (Dr. Jose)
body: Born in Ponta do Sol on March 19, 1874, he is a medical surgeon from the Medical-Surgical School of Lisbon and a medical captain in the army, having enlisted as a second lieutenant on October 21, 1903. He is a member of the General Board of the District and in 1921 was elected senator for Madeira (1922).
